dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) La Crosse County, WI 2014
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for La Crosse County, Wisconsin at 2014. They are feature classes within the geodatabase LaCrosse_Hydro_2014.gdb. The features included in this geodatabase are 'LACROSSE_HYDROLINE_2014' and 'LACROSSE_HYDROPOLY_2014'.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
